data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, built in 2018, offers modern comfort in Winter Haven's Squires Grove. Inside, you'll find an open living area with ample natural light. The kitchen features granite countertops and newer appliances. The master suite includes a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks and a soaking tub. Two additional bedrooms and a second bathroom complete the layout. The backyard is a blank canvas for your ideas. Squires Grove is conveniently located near schools, shopping, and highways. Winter Haven, situated between Tampa and Orlando, is known for its 554 freshwater lakes, ideal for fishing and water sports. It's also part of Florida's Antique Loop, offering antique enthusiasts unique finds. The city's parks and trails showcase Florida's natural beauty. With easy access to Central Florida's attractions and beaches, Winter Haven offers a mix of outdoor adventures and urban conveniences. A great investment or future home in a growing community. Schedule your appointment today!
